               stealing, on the <rs id="t18160918-24-cd137" type="crimeDate">28th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-24-off136 t18160918-24-cd137"></join>, twenty-eight yards of oil-cloth, value 5l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18160918-24-victim306" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Irons
                        <interp inst="t18160918-24-victim306" type="surname" value="Irons"></interp>
