                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160918-24-defend304 t18160918-24-punish141"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 36.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
